    {
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "chapterTitle": "九地篇第十一",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "30478462_14_761-1516",
          "range": "761-1516",
          "rangeStart": 761,
          "rangeEnd": 1516,
          "markText": "孙子曰：用兵之法：有散地、有轻地、有争地、有交地、有衢地、有重地、有氾地、有围地、有死地。诸侯自战其地，为散地①；入人之地而不深者，为轻地②；我得则利，彼得亦利者，为争地③；我可以往，彼可以来者，为交地④；诸侯之地三属，先至而得天下之众者，为衢地⑤；入人之地深，背城邑多者，为重地⑥；行山林、险阻、沮泽，凡难行之道者，为圮地⑦；所由入者隘，所从归者迂，彼寡可以击吾之众者，为围地⑧；疾战则存，不疾战则亡者，为死地⑨。是故散地则无战⑩，轻地则无止⑪，争地则无攻⑫，交地则无绝⑬，衢地则合交⑭，重地则掠⑮，圮地则行⑯，围地则谋⑰，死地则战⑱。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1724049867,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-08-19 14:44:27",
          "chapterUid": 14,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30478462&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=761&rangeEnd=1516",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/acd320b071d1107eacdd451?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=761&rangeEnd=1516"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "chapterTitle": "谋攻篇第三",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "30478462_6_2782-2869",
          "range": "2782-2869",
          "rangeStart": 2782,
          "rangeEnd": 2869,
          "markText": "故上兵伐谋①，其次伐交②，其次伐兵，其下攻城。攻城之法，为不得已。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1662958643,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2022-09-12 12:57:23",
          "chapterUid": 6,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30478462&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2782&rangeEnd=2869",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/acd320b071d1107eacdd451?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2782&rangeEnd=2869"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "30478462_6_1545-1565",
          "range": "1545-1565",
          "rangeStart": 1545,
          "rangeEnd": 1565,
          "markText": "孙子曰：凡用兵之法：全国为上，破国次之；",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1662958614,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2022-09-12 12:56:54",
          "chapterUid": 6,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30478462&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1545&rangeEnd=1565",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/acd320b071d1107eacdd451?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1545&rangeEnd=1565"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "30478462_6_864-1092",
          "range": "864-1092",
          "rangeStart": 864,
          "rangeEnd": 1092,
          "markText": "孙子曰：凡用兵之法：全国为上，破国次之①；全军为上，破军次之②；全旅为上，破旅次之③；全卒为上，破卒次之④；全伍为上，破伍次之⑤。是故百战百胜，非善之善者也；不战而屈人之兵，善之善者也。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1662958602,
